== 功能 ==
HTN3基因表達的初級產物爲組氨素3。[[組氨素|組氨素]]是一類存在於唾液中的富含[[組氨酸|組氨酸]]的[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]，控制其合成的基因位點除了HTN3之外，還有H1N1。組氨素3在合成完畢後，還可以通過蛋白水解轉化成其它的組氨素（比如組氨素4-6）。能控制組氨素3合成的等位基因爲HIS2<ref name="pmid18650243">{{cite journal | author = Oudhoff MJ, Bolscher JG, Nazmi K, Kalay H, van 't Hof W, Amerongen AV, Veerman EC | title = Histatins are the major wound-closure stimulating factors in human saliva as identified in a cell culture assay | journal = FASEB J. | volume = 22 | issue = 11 | pages = 3805–12 |date=November 2008 | pmid = 18650243 | doi = 10.1096/fj.08-112003 | url =  }}</ref>。

